doctype html
html(lang='en')

    head

        meta(charset='utf-8')
        meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no')
        meta(name='description', content='')
        meta(name='author', content='')

        title Polygon

        link(rel='icon', type='image/x-icon', href='assets/img/favicon.ico')

        // Font Awesome icons (free version)
        script(src='https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.15.1/js/all.js', crossorigin='anonymous')

        // Google fonts
        link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Varela+Round', rel='stylesheet')
        link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Nunito:200,200i,300,300i,400,400i,600,600i,700,700i,800,800i,900,900i', rel='stylesheet')

        // Core theme CSS (includes Bootstrap)
        link(href='css/styles.css', rel='stylesheet')

    body#page-top

        // Navigation
        nav#mainNav.navbar.navbar-expand-lg.navbar-light.fixed-top
            .container
                a.navbar-brand.js-scroll-trigger(href='#page-top') Polygon
                button.navbar-toggler.navbar-toggler-right(type='button', data-toggle='collapse', data-target='#navbarResponsive', aria-controls='navbarResponsive', aria-expanded='false', aria-label='Toggle navigation')
                    | Menu
                    i.fas.fa-bars
                #navbarResponsive.collapse.navbar-collapse
                    ul.navbar-nav.ml-auto
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link.js-scroll-trigger(href='#about') About Me
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link.js-scroll-trigger(href='#projects') Projects
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link.js-scroll-trigger(href='#signup') Contact

        // Masthead
        header.masthead
            .container.d-flex.h-100.align-items-center
                .mx-auto.text-center
                    h1.mx-auto.my-0.text-uppercase Polygon
                    h2.text-white-50.mx-auto.mt-2.mb-5 I'm a coding addict.
                    a.btn.btn-primary.js-scroll-trigger(href='#about') About me

        // About
        section#about.about-section.text-center
            .container
                .row
                    .col-lg-8.mx-auto
                        h2.text-white.mb-4 About me
                        p.text-white-50
                            | I'm a person who loves coding. I have experience with JavaScript (Java for short), HyperTextMarkupLanguage (HTML), CascadingStyleSheets and SyntacticallyAwesomeStyleSheets (CSS and SASS), TypeScript (TS) and a bit of C, CS, and C++. 
                            a(href='https://discord.gg/d5R6wCEmAC') I'm also on Discord a lot.

        // Projects
        section#projects.projects-section.bg-light
            .container
                // Featured Project Row
                .row.align-items-center.no-gutters.mb-4.mb-lg-5
                    .col-xl-8.col-lg-7
                        img.img-fluid.mb-3.mb-lg-0(src='assets/img/bg-masthead.jpg', alt='')
                    .col-xl-4.col-lg-5
                        .featured-text.text-center.text-lg-left
                            h4 Shape
                            p.text-black-50.mb-0
                                | Shape is my discord bot that I work a lot on. It's coded in JS. It's still being coded and a dashboard is coming out soon.
                                a(href="https://discord.com/api/oauth2/authorize?client_id=797876566218506265&permissions=8&redirect_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscordshape.herokuapp.com%2Fapi%2Fcallback&scope=bot") This
                                | is the invite.
                // Project One Row
                .row.justify-content-center.no-gutters.mb-5.mb-lg-0
                    .col-lg-6
                        img.img-fluid(src='assets/img/demo-image-01.jpg', alt='')
                    .col-lg-6
                        .bg-black.text-center.h-100.project
                            .d-flex.h-100
                                .project-text.w-100.my-auto.text-center.text-lg-left
                                    h4.text-white Github Website
                                    p.mb-0.text-white-50
                                        | I also have a github website which can be found 
                                        a(href="https://polygonee.github.io") here.
                                        | This shows my github repositories and a few other things. It is responsive and hosted on github pages.
                                    hr.d-none.d-lg-block.mb-0.ml-0
                // Project Two Row
                .row.justify-content-center.no-gutters
                    .col-lg-6
                        img.img-fluid(src='assets/img/demo-image-02.jpg', alt='')
                    .col-lg-6.order-lg-first
                        .bg-black.text-center.h-100.project
                            .d-flex.h-100
                                .project-text.w-100.my-auto.text-center.text-lg-right
                                    h4.text-white Mountains
                                    p.mb-0.text-white-50
                                        | Another example of a project with its respective description. These sections work well responsively as well, try this theme on a small screen!
                                    hr.d-none.d-lg-block.mb-0.mr-0

        // Signup
        section#signup.signup-section
            .container
                .row
                    .col-md-10.col-lg-8.mx-auto.text-center
                        i.far.fa-paper-plane.fa-2x.mb-2.text-white
                        h2.text-white.mb-5 Type something here.
                        form.form-inline.d-flex
                            input#inputEmail.form-control.flex-fill.mr-0.mr-sm-2.mb-3.mb-sm-0(type='eee', placeholder='Enter something...')
                            button.btn.btn-primary.mx-auto(type='href', href='https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dQw4w9WgXcQ') Beam me up

        // Contact
        section.contact-section.bg-black
            .container
                .row
                    .col-md-4.mb-3.mb-md-0
                        .card.py-4.h-100
                            .card-body.text-center
                                i.fas.fa-map-marked-alt.text-primary.mb-2
                                h4.text-uppercase.m-0 Discord Server
                                hr.my-4
                                .small.text-black-50
                                    a(href="https://discord.gg/d5R6wCEmAC") Invite 
                    .col-md-4.mb-3.mb-md-0
                        .card.py-4.h-100
                            .card-body.text-center
                                i.fas.fa-envelope.text-primary.mb-2
                                h4.text-uppercase.m-0 Email
                                hr.my-4
                                .small.text-black-50
                                    a(href='mailto:hi@polygondev.me') hi@polygondev.me
                    .col-md-4.mb-3.mb-md-0
                        .card.py-4.h-100
                            .card-body.text-center
                                i.fas.fa-mobile-alt.text-primary.mb-2
                                h4.text-uppercase.m-0 Phone
                                hr.my-4
                                .small.text-black-50 +1 (420) 420-6969
                .social.d-flex.justify-content-center
                    a.mx-2(href='https://twitter.com/zePolygon')
                        i.fab.fa-twitter
                    a.mx-2(href='https://github.com/polygonee')
                        i.fab.fa-github

        // Footer
        footer.footer.bg-black.small.text-center.text-white-50
            .container
                | Copyright Â© Polygon 2020-2021

        // Bootstrap core JS
        script(src='https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.5.1/jquery.min.js')
        script(src='https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.5.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js')

        // Third party plugin JS
        script(src='https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery-easing/1.4.1/jquery.easing.min.js')

        // Core theme JS
        script(src='js/scripts.js')
